@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div id="vision-and-mission" class="page p-vision-and-mission hidden">
	<div class="fixed-wrapper"></div>
	<div class="js-scroll">
		<main class="page-wrapper">

			<section class="p-vision-and-mission__header" data-prllx="1.5" data-p-no-mask data-p-top>
				<div class="abs background-wrapper">
					<div class="abs background" data-p-elt>
						<div class="abs circle"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="abs eyes" data-prllx="1" data-p-no-mask data-p-top style="opacity: 0 !important;">
					<div class="eyes-wrapper">
						<video class="eyes-loop" autoplay muted playsinline loop>
							<source data-src="/library/videos/fakedot.mp4" type="video/mp4"></source>
						</video>
					</div>
				</div>
				<h1 class="h--1 title">Purpose</h1>
			</section>

			<section class="p-vision-and-mission__vision">
				<div class="block-title" data-prllx=".5" data-p-no-mask>
					<h2 class="title" data-p-elt><b>Small projects,</b> you will be heard</h2>
					<div class="text">
						<p>Great ideas sometimes come from the most unlikely places. But even the best ideas need a way to show the world they exist.</p>
						<p>It is crucial to pave the way for these ideas to succeed. Leveraging the greatest asset of the Cardano network for this purpose is our goal. We have the largest and best crypto community, and we can empower projects while fairly rewarding everyone who chooses to join this revolution.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="block-numbers">
					<h2 class="numbers"><em>0000</em>0000</h2>
					<h3 class="title">MAKERS/CREATORS</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="bird" data-prllx=".8" data-p-no-mask>
					<picture class="r " style="padding-bottom:89.409862570736%" data-ratio="0.89409862570736"><img class="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="/library/media/imagem_site.png" data-srcset="/library/media/imagem_site.png 320w, /library/media/imagem_site.png 640w, /library/media/imagem_site.png 1024w, /library/media/imagem_site.png 1237w" data-sizes="(min-width: 750px) 50vw, 120vw" alt=""></picture>
				</div>
				<div class="title-2">
					<p>Small teams often struggle to promote their ideas, projects, airdrops, tokens, and collections. This is a problem because it limits the network's growth. We are changing this, NOW!</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p--s mentions">
					<p>
						* Easy access for holders of at least one NFT from the SparkPro collection.<br>
						* Anyone with a social media profile can participate in campaigns and earn money.<br>
						* Every project can run marketing campaigns at a price never seen before.<br>
						* The change the Cardano network needed to unlock its community's full potential.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="tablet" data-prllx=".8" data-p-no-mask>
					<picture class="r " style="padding-bottom:64.606376057254%" data-ratio="0.64606376057254"><img class="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://chirpley.ai/library/media/chirpley-plateform.png" data-srcset="https://chirpley.ai/library/media/chirpley-plateform-320x0-c-default.png 320w, https://chirpley.ai/library/media/chirpley-plateform-640x0-c-default.png 640w, https://chirpley.ai/library/media/chirpley-plateform-1024x0-c-default.png 1024w, https://chirpley.ai/library/media/chirpley-plateform-1280x0-c-default.png 1280w, https://chirpley.ai/library/media/chirpley-plateform-1440x0-c-default.png 1440w, https://chirpley.ai/library/media/chirpley-plateform.png 1537w" data-sizes="(min-width: 750px) 80vw, 100vw" alt=""></picture>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="p-vision-and-mission__mission">
				<div class="abs background">
					<div class="t-center circle"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="abs bird" data-prllx=".5" data-p-no-mask style="opacity: 0 !important;">
					<div class="wrapper">
						<video class="eyes-loop lazy" autoplay muted playsinline loop>
							<source data-src="/library/videos/fakedot.mp4" type="video/mp4"></source>
						</video>
						<div class="abs gradient"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<h1 class="h--1 title">TO WORK</h1>
				<h2 class="subtitle">Chirpley wants to create the most effective small influencer marketing platform in the world.</h2>
				<div class="block-logo">
					<div class="f-center logo-wrapper">
						<div class="logo" data-prllx=".8" data-p-no-mask>
							<video class="token-loop lazy" autoplay muted playsinline loop>
								<source data-src="https://chirpley.ai/library/videos/chirpley-token-grey.mp4" type="video/mp4"></source>
							</video>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p--s text">
						<p>Chirpley is the world’s first fully automated, peer-to-peer, all-in-one influencer marketplace totally dedicated to nano and micro-influencers.</p>
						<p>Chirpley will be the one platform that enables end-to-end automated influencing campaigns through Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning and Blockchain technology. We will break down all barriers between small influencers and the marketing community, facilitating absolutely perfect matches with sponsors and brands. No more tiresome negotiating between influencers, marketers and agents. No more mismatched selection of influencers and marketers.</p>
						<p>
							Chirpley applies cutting-edge technology to speed up matchmaking, dealmaking, price setting and campaign launching.<br>
							Chirpley allows marketers to set up 1-click influencer marketing bombs that will see sales take off and earnings soar.
						</p>
						<p>Chirpley is also laying the foundation for the first completely autonomous, decentralized platform, based on blockchain technology and our own Chirpley token.</p>
						<p>Chirpley will take nano- and micro-influencer marketing to the next level. Changing not just the face of influencer marketing, but also the lives of all small influencers who’ll take part in it.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

		</main>

		@await Html.PartialAsync("_Footer")
	</div>
</div>
